        <character char_type="range_value" name="length" from="4" from_unit="mm" to="6" to_unit="mm" />
        <character char_type="range_value" name="width" from="5" from_unit="mm" to="9" to_unit="mm" />
      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="812.txt-7">
      <text>Phyllaries rose-pink to purplish, moderately appressed-villous to puberulous or arachnose, usually viscid-hairy as well (outer phyllaries ovate-acuminate to ovate-lanceolate, lengths 0.5–1 times inner).</text>
      <structure id="o17115" name="phyllary">
